title: How did I not see this...
body:
#YI'S SECRET IDENTITY:

http://i.imgur.com/504QZAP.jpg[\img]

Yes, this post, up to this point, already has not one, not two, but three eye puns.

http://i.imgur.com/tG4UwBX.jpg

\*Cue obligatory Lee-Sin-pun response\*
http://i.imgur.com/kIatZOz.jpg

http://absolute-health.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/peer-pressure.jpg

^ Yes, eyes are a very prominent part of that last image. Shush, you see nothing. (<< You also read nothing.)

P.S. For those of you who didn't need this image of Yi in your brain, remember: what has been seen cannot be unseen. And yes, I know.

https://i.imgflip.com/zw1b2.jpg

... I'll stop now.

replies.body:
Yi gotta be kiddin' me. Wuju please come up with better puns next time?

Eye see what you were going for though.
* I garen-tee your out of puns

Much to your own miss fortune I believe that your garan-tee is in vayne because I believe that you meant to say "you're" and not "your" -ick.

Okay that ending one was more than just a bit of a stretch but deal with it because by my knight's vow there shall be no redemption for you here on this day, not even your guardian angel can save you now. Wow, I'm on a roll here actually... Better change my name to Rammus. XD

Ya know, I actually only intended to make a thread about Yi's secret identity, but the meme got out of hand, then everything around the meme got out of hand, then this was interpreted as a pun thread, then as a pun thread it was interpreted as meh.

\*sniffle\*

Live and learn folks.

Yi just wishes that was who he is cuz that is Jax's secret identity.
